<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>رَوى عنْهُ حمادُ بنُ سلمةَ، مُرسلٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٩٧٧٤]</span> فُضَيْلٌ، رَجُلٌ مِنْ بَني عُذْرَةَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى عنه أيوبُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سمِع سالمَ بنَ عبدِ اللَّهِ بنِ عُمرَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
